title: Bitwise to launch two Ether-themed ETFs Monday
description: Beginning Oct. 2, Bitwise's ETFs will allow investors to tap into the burgeoning Chicago Mercantile Exchange Ethereum futures market via a regulated ETF format.

title: Vitalik Buterin cautions against staking pools adopting DAOs
